      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chachapalli yohyohualtic tlen ihtipahpatlactic huan achi huahcapantzitzin huan nochipa tzinyohyohualtic huan quemmantzin quipiya imahmah zo ce itentzaucca.</Note_Text>
